        "subject": "LU-7324 lnet: dedicated retval for delayed message",
        "message": "LU-7324 lnet: dedicated retval for delayed message\n\nA delayed message can be handled and released by another thread\nat anytime after releasing lock. This patch adds a dedicated\nreturn value for delayed message to avoid checking of message\nstatus after releasing lock.\n\nSigned-off-by: Liang Zhen <liang.zhen@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I78de05df093501e14876f338289a4e8e62d529cb\n"
      },
